{"tid":567432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"坐的士拾iPhone 7歸還 人夫遭基督徒物主爆樽","createTime":"2018-02-21T00:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T06:01:36.000Z","uid":65346,"like":10,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2134927180fc3c4b546ea262c2efdde20dc252aa","tid":567432,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T00:02:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180221/57856205\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180221%2F57856205&d=CWRTqE1GfqspQNwmIOWEoDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=3fcbbeb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180221%2F57856205&h=62ed9313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180221/57856205</a><br />\n<br />\n紅磡德民街近船塢街發生傷人案，凌晨3時許，一名姓張33歲男子，遭約4名男子圍毆，事主受傷致電報警，稱較早前與姓沈33歲妻子，乘的士從尖沙嘴返回紅磡住所途中，在座椅上撿獲一部iPhone 7手機，其後電話響起遂相約機主取回手機，夫婦當到達約定地點等候交收期間，機主及數名教友突衝出用啤酒樽向他施襲毆打，並將手機奪回，四散逃去，救護員趕至將傷者送院治理，警方正展開調查。"},{"pid":"0ce0b91332195b0636411d5cec2d654f4229b04b","tid":567432,"uid":36238,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T00:03:09.000Z","msg":"想打救佢啫"},{"pid":"411d84accc3d7cbf3363c031d438b72121309fb3","tid":567432,"uid":3454,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T00:03:44.000Z","msg":"神嘅考驗/安排"},{"pid":"9ebdd5703d8be768a19c8ec5d2033c82bf446fe7","tid":567432,"uid":59612,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T00:03:57.000Z","msg":"朋友 上帝會原諒你的<br />\n但我手入面個玻璃樽唔會！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk